Language name: Sinhalese
Language number: 2020
Alternate names: Sinhala
Classification: Indo-European, Indic

Comments: Sinhala is spoken in all parts of Sri Lanka, 
also in Singapore and Thailand.
 
Sources: 
Coates, W.A. and da Silva, M.W.S. 1960. The segmental 
phonemes of Sinhalese. University of Ceylon Review 18: 
163-75.